text: Haug's worm lizard (Cynisca haugi) is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is endemic to Gabon. ==References== Category:Cynisca (lizard) Category:Reptiles described in 1904 Category:Taxa named by François Mocquard Category:Endemic fauna of Gabon Category:Reptiles of Gabon
title: Haug's worm lizard
